{"tid":57382,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朱千雪獨身過聖誕 曝正日偕王浩信高踭鞋打籃球","createTime":"2016-12-28T03:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T03:50:59.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fac167eed1d4cdc84cdf7c1a4976efa62c7c3980","tid":57382,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161228/large/28ec1p18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161228%2Flarge%2F28ec1p18.jpg&h=ddff86bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪與張彥博昨日到將軍澳出席聖誕活動，分別獻唱和玩遊戲。朱千雪謂聖誕於工作中度過：「聖誕節嗰日，我、王浩信、張振朗同蔡思貝趁放飯去左隔籬籃球場打波，平時我跑步多，所以最渣係我，不過我都原諒自己，因為我着住高踭鞋打。」預料明天巿區最低氣温將繼續下降至大約12度她謂希望每年暑假及冬天都可拍劇，又賣口乖感謝監製等她放假才開拍。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161228/large/28ec1p17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161228%2Flarge%2F28ec1p17.jpg&h=04df9417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問到除夕可有活動吸金？熱刺聖徒「和」味濃正修讀法律的朱千雪說：「都有活動同annual dinner邀請，我都想搵多啲錢，因為學費好貴，自己又想讀多幾個課程，早啲可以畢業。」張彥博則表示聖誕同樣開工，近日多了商場演出，可以趁機吸金。"},{"pid":"ce67deea99a37eca33871a84ff20ce6daf82483f","tid":57382,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:18:40.000Z","msg":"下面張相摸住個閪做咩"},{"pid":"cee60d4631e4d18c2aa1c55b8bb958175a241214","tid":57382,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:28:47.000Z","msg":"熱刺聖徒「和」味濃？"},{"pid":"a7005c22f0003ca29e02b4f8f6870d5286cc1c5c","tid":57382,"uid":36501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:31:02.000Z","msg":"巴打改左名?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cfeb48769f669dc6c97cb90dddc6854e864db3","tid":57382,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,